choices.text: You are given a line of length $n$ and you want to divide it into several non-empty sections. The value of $i$-th element is $a_i$. You want to generate the maximum number of sections from the list. There is a restriction for each section: the number of values in the section multiplied by the minimum value among all values in the section must be at least $x$. Each value should belong to at most one section. Some value may be left without being part of any section.
